# Tera Filters Reference

Tera supports many built-in filters for transforming variables.

## String Case Filters

- `snake_case`: Convert to snake_case
- `pascal_case`: Convert to PascalCase
- `camel_case`: Convert to camelCase
- `capitalize`: Capitalize first character
- `upper`: Convert to UPPERCASE
- `lower`: Convert to lowercase
- `trim`: Remove whitespace

## Usage

Apply filters with the pipe operator:

```tera
{{ variable_name | filter_name }}
```

## Examples

```tera
{{ "UserService" | snake_case }}       // user_service
{{ "user_service" | pascal_case }}     // UserService
{{ "hello" | capitalize }}              // Hello
{{ "HELLO" | lower }}                   // hello
```
